02-11T06:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾時有統一</blockquote><br />\n姐係有個共識<br />\n都係以「飯」作為主食糧</blockquote><br />\n鬼佬食飯㗎咩</blockquote><br />\n意大利飯係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主食嚟㗎咩？佢哋又代表到幾多人？</blockquote><br />\n未係 咁計唔好話華人主食係包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n華人都食叉燒包奶黃包</blockquote><br />\n唔好講其他地方,中國北方主要食糧都未必係米啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你叫D食開麵嘅情何以堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89593d23fce9dc84580c2b5c7a76c9982fd23acb","tid":116083,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">古時既人獵殺野獸作主食糧</span><br />\n究竟從咩時候人類統一以「飯」作為主食糧？<br />\n點解有咁多穀類食物唔選擇係要選中「飯」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個assumption點嚟<br />\n人類primate近親好主要都係雜食性<br />\n祖先應該都會挖野果同野薯之類嘅嘢食<br />\n但好奇嘅位點解人會揀米，麥呢啲穀物<br />\n有殼好麻煩又唔大粒嘅嘢嚟種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5163855b888c64b9f69afbea7c245ab9f02ee8d7","tid":116083,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:23:28.000Z","msg":"錯唔晒嘅<br />\n加拿大鬼佬都好鍾意食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66a9c13476ae198d3bed1db8eb739a9eaf250ee","tid":116083,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:25:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4748fede92a90038203b123cb7c724e82abf383","tid":116083,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:25:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錯唔晒嘅<br />\n加拿大鬼佬都好鍾意食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都好中意食魚生 咁魚生係咪我主食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd09769af6851f854ab820501e97772258c25119","tid":116083,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錯唔晒嘅<br />\n加拿大鬼佬都好鍾意食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我鐘意食魚生唔得如我主食係魚生喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd8e6172271615b4d7e8e8cca45dd1abb7488ed","tid":116083,"uid":34828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:26:27.000Z","msg":"未來"},{"pid":"317409149ced9eaa4c464060eb65609859b7284a","tid":116083,"uid":55712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如話由幾時開始糙米飯變左做精製白飯、白麵、白麵包<br />\n呢d累唔少人，不過醫學範疇就無謂係度討論</blockquote><br />\n你有冇食過糙米？<br />\n當有錢嗰時有邊個唔想食白米"},{"pid":"6f5de92c457dbd567fd83126c33d63d1ff137e9d","tid":116083,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">古時既人獵殺野獸作主食糧</span><br />\n究竟從咩時候人類統一以「飯」作為主食糧？<br />\n點解有咁多穀類食物唔選擇係要選中「飯」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個assumption點嚟<br />\n人類primate近親好主要都係雜食性<br />\n祖先應該都會挖野果同野薯之類嘅嘢食<br />\n但好奇嘅位點解人會揀米，麥呢啲穀物<br />\n有殼好麻煩又唔大粒嘅嘢嚟種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n薯仔之類要等發現美洲先有<br />\n唔種五殼粟米種乜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77537aafbff4071174f6edb1cd96be0612352016","tid":116083,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:30:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f312ee6c71622100f5e71d2b921e144fb9c56f9b","tid":116083,"uid":55712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算你想講農耕文化都唔係到到work啦<br />\n你當蒙古死既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2981471eddb6f7e44ca1a3876fe24498bad9f0c3","tid":116083,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac4cb6ce776d7cf355a56eb74e6b76a39780261","tid":116083,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:35:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錯唔晒嘅<br />\n加拿大鬼佬都好鍾意食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鍾意同主食係兩回事"},{"pid":"506ec1e18726858013e13b6524defed29fe1d1c7","tid":116083,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">古時既人獵殺野獸作主食糧</span><br />\n究竟從咩時候人類統一以「飯」作為主食糧？<br />\n點解有咁多穀類食物唔選擇係要選中「飯」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個assumption點嚟<br />\n人類primate近親好主要都係雜食性<br />\n祖先應該都會挖野果同野薯之類嘅嘢食<br />\n但好奇嘅位點解人會揀米，麥呢啲穀物<br />\n有殼好麻煩又唔大粒嘅嘢嚟種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n薯仔之類要等發現美洲先有<br />\n唔種五殼粟米種乜<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我指係番薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就係唔明點解要種米麥唔種多啲粟米同番薯"},{"pid":"afbe44e0377bd4c1025764f65c9d542985d7bc75","tid":116083,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c465a3a2d8dc9c98fd37abf8c05ad34896dc1b38","tid":116083,"uid":33361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:00:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如話由幾時開始糙米飯變左做精製白飯、白麵、白麵包<br />\n呢d累唔少人，不過醫學範疇就無謂係度討論</blockquote><br />\n你有冇食過糙米？<br />\n當有錢嗰時有邊個唔想食白米</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n糙米好食wor, 比白米更有口感"},{"pid":"5e441e5609eba82fb0370c1fdc3e3fa3a5a5bf0f","tid":116083,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi